	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vir clarissime, rarius omnino scribo, quam vellem; sed hoc facit nuncciorum penuria.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribo nunc, quia <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l441">Schafusianus</placeName> nuncius se obtulit.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pulchre valeo, dei benignitate, ac laboro more meo.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verti librum <persName ref="p458" cert="high">Brentii</persName> contra <persName type="citizen_name">Asotum</persName>, ac fere iam typis excussus.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam Italice intelligeres; non pauca enim addidi, sed consulto autore.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Avellar hinc proxima septimana, ut spero, futurus partim <placeName ref="l496" cert="high">Stutgardiae</placeName>, partim in quodam oppido, cui nomen <placeName type="auto_name">Bachenae</placeName>, ubi dominus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20206">Gribaldus</persName> profitetur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germania</placeName> bene haberet, quod ad religionem attinet, nisi hinc <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8441" cert="high">Svenchfeldiani</persName>, inde amarus zelus in articulo eucharistico eam proscinderet; det pacem dominus ecclesiis suis.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Omnino futura sunt comitia mense martio <placeName ref="l410" cert="high">Ratisbonae</placeName> pro expeditione scilicet in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turcas</placeName> suscipienda; iam enim, quanquam sit hyems, excursiones faciunt in <placeName ref="l882" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Hungaria</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Intra octo dies sumus habituri conventum totius circuli <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2481">Suevici</placeName> hic <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l412" cert="high">Reutlingae</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Princeps noster venit hodie in proximum pagum venaturus, dum veniat dies negociis statutus.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fui cum illo aliquandiu; inimicus homo multa instillavit in eius aures de <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Calvino</persName>, cui certe undique video non paucos esse adversarios.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si forte e <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Berna</placeName> venit imago a <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4191" cert="high">Matthia Apiario</persName>, cura illa <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l441">Schaphusam</placeName> ad <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2757" cert="high">Rugerum</persName> nostrum; si nondum missa est, urge <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerum</persName>, ut Apiarium, qui iam praecium tulit, urgeat.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mitto aliquot imagines cum Germanico elogio; hac alea scilicet ludo, cum a gravioribus studiis quiescendum est.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salvere iubeo dominum <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gualterum</persName> ac tuostris generos ac reliquos fratres.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">iuvate me precibus vestris, quod vos valde rogo.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l412" cert="high">Reutlingae</placeName> 6. decembris 1555.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In hoc conventu quaeretur, quo modo <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2481">Suevia</placeName> sit parata preditibus, equitibus, bombardis etc., si pugnandum esset.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc caput.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p3375" cert="high">Vergerius</persName> frater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">(A. H.) Clarissimo viro domino <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Henrico Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinae</placeName> ecclesiae antistiti, fratri honorando.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
